<pre class="sh_perl">        $o_vac-&#62;process($o_main_internet, [h_test]);</pre>

<dt><a name="cleanup"
>cleanup</a></dt>

<dd>
<p>Cleanup replied-to dbs based on (now - expirytime) or optionally given date. All entries older than given date will be removed, to clean a file, you can empty it by giving a date of, for example, &#39;99999999&#39;.</p>

<pre class="sh_perl">        $o_vac-&#62;cleanup($date, [opt_a_ref_addresses]);</pre>

